instruction: Make a shopping list for a healthy dinner that serves 4 people.
output:
Shopping List:
- 4 boneless, skinless chicken breasts 
- 2 large sweet potatoes 
- 2 avocados 
- 1 bunch of broccoli 
- 1 red bell pepper 
- 1 can of black beans 
- 1 box of quinoa 
- Olive oil 
- Salt & pepper 
- Lemon juice
